
0. Quick instal

	$ git clone https://github.com/disco-v8/EvServer.git
	$ cd EvServer

	$ autoheader
	$ aclocal
	$ automake --add-missing --copy
	$ autoconf

	$ make clean
	$ ./configure --prefix=/usr
	$ make

1. Usage:

    $ ./evserver [/PATH/TO/evserver.ini]

If you don't specify a "evserver.ini", it will only listen on UNIX domain sockets.

2. How to connect to EvServer

In case of Unix domain socket

	$ nc -U /tmp/.EvServer.sock

"nc" is Ncat. (https://nmap.org/ncat) 

3. Thanks

libev, OpenSSL, Ncat, VSCode :-)
	...and everyone!
